comments: Porzingis (WAS) legally contests Collins' (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Porzingis (WAS) grasps and then quickly releases Murray's (ATL) left arm as the pick is set.
Murray (ATL) brings his right hand to Beal's (WAS) right side and marginal contact occurs as Beal elevates for the shot attempt.
Kispert (WAS) and Collins (ATL) engage and disengage with one another near the block, and marginal contact occurs prior to the shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Hunter (ATL) bats the rebound, gains full control of the ball, and legally starts his dribble as he turns along the baseline.

Beal (WAS) moves laterally and initiates more than marginal contact with Hunter's (ATL) arm during the drive. The contact occurs prior to Hunter's gather and continuation should not have been awarded.
Kispert (WAS) establishes himself in Murray's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the defensive switch simultaneously occurs.
Collins (ATL) engages and disengages with Porzingis (WAS) as Porzingis moves to set the pick.
Porzingis (WAS) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Hunter's (ATL) path does not deliver illegal contact as the pick is set.
Beal (WAS) releases his off-arm away from Hunter's (ATL) side and does not apply any force as he shifts his momentum at the end of the drive.
Hunter (ATL) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Beal (WAS) and is not in a legal guarding position when body contact occurs during Beal's upward shooting motion.
Beal (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Young (ATL) on the wing.
Young (ATL) brings his forearms toward Beal's (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs as Beal starts his dribble following the change of possession.
Young (ATL) rests his left hand on Beal's (WAS) right side and retracts it away without applying any force after Beal's gather.
Young (ATL) initiates contact across Avdija's (WAS) right arm and causes Avdija to lose control of the ball in the lane.
Beal (WAS) brings his right arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Young's (ATL) front as Young splits the double team.
Kuzma (WAS) delivers body contact to Hunter (ATL) and affects Hunter's layup attempt.
Beal (WAS) gathers the pass and takes more than two steps before coming to a stop in the corner.
Avdija (WAS) briefly has his arm around Young's (ATL) upper half and quickly slides it off during the inbound.
Wright (WAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Hunter (ATL) is moving somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with Kuzma (WAS) as Kuzma changes direction during the drive.
Collins (ATL) brings his hands forward toward Kuzma's (WAS) back and marginal contact occurs during the layup attempt.
Kispert (WAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Kuzma (WAS) establishes himself in Capela's (ATL) path and, after they each initially engage with one another, Kuzma does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen.
Murray (ATL) legally contests Porzingis' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
